{"tid":1946330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[淨返唔夠三日]痴線同我入嚟簽聯署！名校校友會(紅底)依個時勢仲想喺酒店搞AGM!?!","createTime":"2020-03-27T14:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T14:12:22.000Z","uid":312626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7127eae71480b3bc9ded4b0babcbaca8ca871efc","tid":1946330,"uid":312626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T14:12:22.000Z","msg":"好簡單來講<br />\n聖保羅男女校友會同校董會都<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好藍</span></strong>：<br />\n成員有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">廣東省政協</span></span>etc(自己check)<br />\n<br />\n校董會之前出信，<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔俾學生喺學校入邊搞政治活動</span>，否則記過(而校友會嘅人好多都係校董)<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191031/s00001/1572460465668/聖保羅男女校董會發信-擅辦政治活動會處分\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191031%2Fs00001%2F1572460465668%2F%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1-%E6%93%85%E8%BE%A6%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%83%E8%99%95%E5%88%86&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=1cd878c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191031%2Fs00001%2F1572460465668%2F%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1-%E6%93%85%E8%BE%A6%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%83%E8%99%95%E5%88%86&h=a9a13025\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191031/s00001/1572460465668/聖保羅男女校董會發信-擅辦政治活動會處分</a><br />\n<br />\n本來年年都自動當選，但今年竟然有<span style=\"color: gold;\">五個黃絲候選人</span>出嚟選，驚到佢哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇原因</span></span>咁延遲開個會員大會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200102/CIACHJWTBFDQKLTEOMODFQI7DY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200102%2FCIACHJWTBFDQKLTEOMODFQI7DY%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=fd9b279b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200102%2FCIACHJWTBFDQKLTEOMODFQI7DY%2F&h=3caaa91f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200102/CIACHJWTBFDQKLTEOMODFQI7DY/</a><br />\n<br />\n拖到而家有武漢肺炎，但竟然破先例想喺洲際酒店搞AGM。你去唔到呀？寫授權書囉，死都要搞個會。會員8100個，book咁大個場，當有50個人嚟，<span style=\"color: red;\">酒店有幾多個外國返嚟嘅人喺度自我隔離啊</span>？萬一有事，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尖沙咀仲唔大爆發</span></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n所以有人搞個聯署，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">市民都可以入嚟簽得</span>(文筆幾好)，依加先得三百個簽名，我係個校友會我都唔理你照搞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔夠三日喳！幫手入嚟簽個名啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd90Jr4XgabgXsL8fgV2ES6ShKpapj9-22DTBanELyLY0i5Dg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSd90Jr4XgabgXsL8fgV2ES6ShKpapj9-22DTBanELyLY0i5Dg%2Fviewform&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=522c4a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd90Jr4XgabgXsL8fgV2ES6ShKpapj9-22DTBanELyLY0i5Dg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知酒店ballroom林鄭比唔比，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都同我簽咗先！！！</span>"}]}